-- South Africa Beats England by an Innings in First Cricket Test
-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 2012-07-23T14:59:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-23/south-africa-beats-england-by-an-innings-in-first-cricket-test.html
South Africa  beat England by an
innings and 12 runs in the first cricket Test at the Oval in
London today.  England was dismissed for 240 in its second innings, having
totaled 385 in the first. South Africa had declared on 637-2.  There are three matches in the series.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter-Joseph Hegarty at 
 phegarty@bloomberg.net  